Package: mdview
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libwebkitgtk-6.0-4
Description: Lightweight, keyboard-driven markdown viewer for Linux
 A minimal, read-only, CLI-first markdown viewer. Opens a local .md file
 (or stdin) in a native window and renders it with syntax highlighting.
 Supports GFM tables, task lists, dark/light themes, live reload on save,
 and keyboard zoom. No editing, no bloat — just clean reading.
